<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Welcome to KicksFactory!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .header img {
            max-width: 150px;
        }
        
        .content {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: flex; 
            padding: 0.375rem 0.75rem; 
            justify-content: center; 
            border-radius: 0.375rem; 
            width: 50%; 
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            line-height: 1.25rem; 
            font-weight: 600; 
            color: #ffffff; 
            background-color: #f97316; /* Tailwind orange-600 */
            text-decoration: none;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <svg width="100" height="100" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><text x="50%" y="50%" font-family="Arial" font-size="48" fill="#F97316" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="middle">K</text></svg>
            <h1>Welcome to KicksFactory!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{reciever}},</p>
            <p>Thank you for joining KicksFactory, your go-to destination for the latest and greatest sneakers. We're thrilled to have you with us!</p>
            <p>With KicksFactory, you'll have access to exclusive sneaker drops, special offers, and the best collection of kicks available.</p>
            <p>Get started now and discover your next favorite pair of sneakers!</p>
            <p>
                <a href="{{url}}/signin" class="cta-button">Sign In</a>
            </p>
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to contact our support team at support@kicksfactory.com.</p>
            <p>Happy shopping!</p>
            <p>The KicksFactory Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
